text:
here’s a quick conversion of the legacy float grid:
```.row-fluid {
  display: flex;
  margin: -1rem;
}

.row-fluid [class*="span"] {
  margin: 1rem;
  flex: 0 1 auto;
}

.row-fluid .span12 {
  flex-basis: 100%;
}

.row-fluid .span11 {
  flex-basis: 91.66666663%;
}

.row-fluid .span10 {
  flex-basis: 83.3333333%;
}

.row-fluid .span9 {
  flex-basis: 74.468085099%;
}

.row-fluid .span8 {
  flex-basis: 66.66666664%;
}

.row-fluid .span7 {
  flex-basis: 58.33333331%;
}

.row-fluid .span6 {
  flex-basis: 49.99999998%;
}

.row-fluid .span5 {
  flex-basis: 41.66666665%;
}

.row-fluid .span4 {
  flex-basis: 33.33333332%;
}

.row-fluid .span3 {
  flex-basis: 24.99999999%;
}

.row-fluid .span2 {
  flex-basis: 16.66666666%;
}

.row-fluid .span1 {
  flex-basis: 8.33333333%;
}

@media (max-width: 767px) {
  .row-fluid {
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .row-fluid [class*="span"] {
    flex-basis: 100%;
  }
}```
